questions.scenario:
You are debugging a production issue where a Spring Boot application deployed on an external servlet container experiences a progressive increase in Metaspace usage after every hot-redeployment, eventually throwing `java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: Metaspace`. You locate the following custom context listener snippet:

java
public class CustomContextListener implements ServletContextListener {
    private static final ThreadLocal<CustomConfiguration> configLocal = new ThreadLocal<>();

    @Override
    public void contextInitialized(ServletContextEvent sce) {
        configLocal.set(new CustomConfiguration());
    }

    @Override
    public void contextDestroyed(ServletContextEvent sce) {
        // Context is undeployed/destroyed
    }
}
